title: Negative Calorie Soup
directions: Combine all ingredients in a stock pot and bring to a boil.
Add water, if needed, to cover all vegetables.
Reduce heat to a moderate simmer and cover.
Cook about 1 hour, or until all vegetables are tender.
ingredients: 1 head green cabbage, cut into 1 inch pieces
4 turnips, peeled and cut into cubes
2 zucchini, peeled and cut into cubes
32 ounces beef stock or chicken stock, or 16 ounces tomato juice and 16 ounces water
